import React from 'react';
import { Box, Heading } from 'grommet';

const landing = props => {
  return (

      {/* <Box height="45%" justify="end" animation="fadeIn">

          size="small" 
        >

        <Heading 
          color="status-warning" 
          textAlign="center"
          size="large" 
        >
          {props.location}
        </Heading>
      </Box> */}

      <Box height="100%" justify="center" align="center" animation="fadeIn">

}

export default landing;
